Megatron Revived:
 
He sighed and put his sword back on his back.  Before coming here, he had developed a taste for terran music, specifically from a series of entertainment called Hellsing.  He had a small media player with a small but powerful speaker always with him and took it out of a compartment and started playing the morbid and eery music in the hall, easing his tension a bit.
